headline: This BlackRock ETF Could Soar 12,770%, According to Billionaire Michael Saylor
summary: BlackRock introduced an incredibly popular ETF early in 2024 that now has over $70 billion in assets.  The price of the asset this ETF owns could rise almost 12,800% in 20 years, according to billionaire Michael Saylor.  Michael Saylor, the tech entrepreneur who founded the enterprise software provider Strategy (formerly known as MicroStrategy), has a net worth estimated at $9.3 billion.
